00947 inline void
00948 RMSubRoute::getExternal(uint32 index,
00949                         uint32 &mapID,
00950                         uint32 &nodeID,
00951                         uint32 &cost,
00952                         uint32 &estimatedCost,
00953                         int32& lat,
00954                         int32& lon,
00955                         uint32& costASum,
00956                         uint32& costBSum,
00957                         uint32& costCSum)
00958 {
00959    mapID         = m_extMapID[index];
00960    nodeID        = m_extNodeID[index];
00961    cost          = m_extCost[index];
00962    estimatedCost = m_extEstimatedCost[index];
00963    lat           = m_lats[index];
00964    lon           = m_lons[index];
00965    costASum      = m_costsA[index];
00966    costBSum      = m_costsB[index];
00967    costCSum      = m_costsC[index];
00968 }
00969 
00970 inline void
00971 RMSubRoute::getCostSums(uint32 index,
00972                         uint32& costA,
00973                         uint32& costB,
00974                         uint32& costC)
00975 {
00976    if ( index < m_costsA.getSize() ) {
00977       costA = m_costsA[index];
00978       costB = m_costsB[index];
00979       costC = m_costsC[index];
00980    } else {
00981       mc2log << error << "RMSR: Reading costs outside vector " << endl;
00982       costA = costB = costC = 0;
00983    }
00984 }
00985 
00986 inline void
00987 RMSubRoute::getExternal(uint32 index,
00988                         uint32 &mapID,
00989                         uint32 &nodeID,
00990                         uint32 &cost,
00991                         uint32 &estimatedCost)
00992 {
00993    int32 lat,lon;
00994    uint32 dummy;
00995    getExternal(index, mapID, nodeID, cost, estimatedCost, lat, lon, dummy,
00996                dummy, dummy);
00997 }
